1
00:00:44,362 --> 00:00:49,137
=The Hidden Heir Ye Chen=
(Adapted from "The Peerless Son-in-Law")

2
00:00:49,650 --> 00:00:52,225
=Episode 20=

3
00:00:53,425 --> 00:00:55,025
We really appreciate the thought,

4
00:00:55,212 --> 00:00:56,759
but these gifts are just too valuable.

5
00:00:56,759 --> 00:00:57,712
We can't accept them.

6
00:00:57,850 --> 00:00:59,330
Please, take them back with you.

7
00:00:59,500 --> 00:01:00,719
I'm following her lead on this.

8
00:01:01,570 --> 00:01:02,840
Please, take these back with you.

9
00:01:03,225 --> 00:01:05,320
I'm just a simple house husband.

10
00:01:05,320 --> 00:01:06,539
I'm not looking for much else.

11
00:01:06,910 --> 00:01:08,719
I'm happy just being the man
behind my wife.

12
00:01:09,719 --> 00:01:11,580
Mr. Ye, don't be so quick
to count yourself out.

13
00:01:11,599 --> 00:01:12,950
Give it some thought.

14
00:01:13,079 --> 00:01:15,175
The offer is yours
whenever you're ready.

15
00:01:16,439 --> 00:01:17,760
You're giving up already?

16
00:01:17,760 --> 00:01:18,900
I see the commitment level.

17
00:01:19,120 --> 00:01:19,760
Mr. Ye,

18
00:01:20,200 --> 00:01:20,840
Mrs. Ye,

19
00:01:21,075 --> 00:01:21,795
goodbye.

20
00:01:26,640 --> 00:01:27,159
Master.

21
00:01:27,429 --> 00:01:28,400
She's out of the way now.

22
00:01:28,640 --> 00:01:30,359
Ms. Qin, you've only just recovered.

23
00:01:30,460 --> 00:01:32,040
You should head home and get some rest.

24
00:01:37,139 --> 00:01:38,350
I'll see you again very soon.

25
00:01:44,780 --> 00:01:45,599
You were incredible.

26
00:01:45,760 --> 00:01:47,200
You handled that perfectly.

27
00:01:47,439 --> 00:01:48,359
Incredible, huh?

28
00:01:48,360 --> 00:01:50,099
There goes a fortune,
right out the door!

29
00:01:50,319 --> 00:01:51,680
That gemstone was massive.

30
00:01:52,079 --> 00:01:53,879
If I'd worn that in front
of Qian Hongyan,

31
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:55,640
she would've been green with envy!

32
00:01:56,025 --> 00:01:56,719
Chen,

33
00:01:56,959 --> 00:01:57,959
what have you been up to?

34
00:01:57,959 --> 00:02:00,920
Why are all these elite families
making you these incredible offers?

35
00:02:01,862 --> 00:02:03,367
It must be because of Wang Daokun.

36
00:02:03,920 --> 00:02:06,175
They know he and Wang Dongxue are,

37
00:02:06,239 --> 00:02:07,000
well, connected.

38
00:02:07,010 --> 00:02:09,400
So they're just coming through me
to get a foot in the door

39
00:02:09,920 --> 00:02:11,040
at Dihao Group, that's all.

40
00:02:12,159 --> 00:02:13,760
That makes no sense at all.

41
00:02:14,439 --> 00:02:17,050
Those families are
plenty powerful on their own.

42
00:02:17,599 --> 00:02:18,360
Well...

43
00:02:18,680 --> 00:02:19,560
You see...

44
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:26,360
Dihao is about to launch
a massive new project.

45
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:28,887
Both families naturally want
a piece of the pie.

46
00:02:29,560 --> 00:02:30,479
It's all confidential.

47
00:02:30,539 --> 00:02:32,080
Stop grilling him for business secrets.

48
00:02:32,080 --> 00:02:34,199
Forget about business secrets.

49
00:02:34,199 --> 00:02:36,439
My heart is still breaking over
that huge gemstone.

50
00:02:36,439 --> 00:02:37,680
Listen to me, Chen,

51
00:02:37,879 --> 00:02:39,120
the business world is cutthroat.

52
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:40,800
Those families are dangerous players.

53
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:42,400
We can't afford to get caught

54
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:43,840
in the middle of their schemes.

55
00:02:44,879 --> 00:02:45,599
You're right, Dad.

56
00:02:59,639 --> 00:03:00,599
Honey.

57
00:03:01,587 --> 00:03:04,080
Don't you think it's time
we make this marriage the real thing?

58
00:03:06,960 --> 00:03:08,159
I think Dad has a point.

59
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:10,080
You're becoming

60
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:11,599
quite the hot commodity.

61
00:03:12,319 --> 00:03:14,759
First the Qin heiress shows up
seeking your mentorship,

62
00:03:14,759 --> 00:03:17,390
then the Song family head personally
comes knocking to recruit you.

63
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:17,919
Normally,

64
00:03:18,639 --> 00:03:21,080
women of that status are untouchable,

65
00:03:21,080 --> 00:03:23,300
but today, they were both competing
for your attention.

66
00:03:24,159 --> 00:03:25,120
It got me thinking

67
00:03:25,539 --> 00:03:26,680
maybe this life is too small

68
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:29,360
a stage for a man of your caliber.

69
00:03:30,790 --> 00:03:31,960
Especially since this marriage

70
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:33,919
was never your choice to begin with.

71
00:03:34,639 --> 00:03:35,719
Mr. Ye.

72
00:03:36,919 --> 00:03:38,039
Care to rethink our marriage?

73
00:03:38,039 --> 00:03:39,039
What is there to rethink?

74
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:40,960
You've become quite the big deal lately.

75
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:42,599
Guess I'll take the floor now.

76
00:03:43,199 --> 00:03:43,800
No, no, no!

77
00:03:43,879 --> 00:03:44,520
Don't say that.

78
00:03:44,879 --> 00:03:45,879
I'd never allow that.

79
00:03:46,080 --> 00:03:47,960
Heiress or not, I only have eyes for you.

80
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:50,560
Sure, our marriage started out fake,

81
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:51,280
but...

82
00:03:51,599 --> 00:03:52,599
But my feelings aren't.

83
00:03:52,599 --> 00:03:53,919
You must know that by now.

84
00:03:55,439 --> 00:03:56,520
You have no idea how much

85
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:58,650
it meant when you called me
"honey" today.

86
00:03:58,662 --> 00:04:01,287
♪Like a wandering cloud in the sky♪

87
00:04:01,879 --> 00:04:02,439
Just kidding.

88
00:04:03,919 --> 00:04:05,039
I'm happy

89
00:04:05,039 --> 00:04:06,039
you're thriving,

90
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:07,439
but that's exactly

91
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:10,080
what worries me.

92
00:04:10,439 --> 00:04:11,439
I worry

93
00:04:11,639 --> 00:04:12,719
about your safety.

94
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:14,479
I worry

95
00:04:15,479 --> 00:04:16,520
we will

96
00:04:16,520 --> 00:04:17,719
drift apart.

97
00:04:18,159 --> 00:04:19,080
Most of all, I worry

98
00:04:19,719 --> 00:04:21,080
you'll regret ever choosing me.

99
00:04:22,125 --> 00:04:23,987
♪The rain echoes my longing♪

100
00:04:24,075 --> 00:04:25,600
♪Ticking on until the dawn♪

101
00:04:25,662 --> 00:04:28,720
♪Again and again
it reminds my heart of you♪

102
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:29,519
Things might change,

103
00:04:30,199 --> 00:04:31,560
but the way I feel never will.

104
00:04:32,520 --> 00:04:33,560
And I'll never regret us.

105
00:04:33,650 --> 00:04:36,937
♪Yet I never see the end
of this downpour♪

106
00:04:37,079 --> 00:04:37,959
Yeah, I don't buy it.

107
00:04:38,199 --> 00:04:39,120
Fine.

108
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:40,680
Then let me make you a proposal

109
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:41,720
to convince you.

110
00:04:43,460 --> 00:04:44,319
What kind of proposal?

111
00:04:44,400 --> 00:04:45,600
♪Can you hear the voice of my heart?♪

112
00:04:45,639 --> 00:04:46,639
When are we going

113
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:48,920
to renew our marriage contract?

114
00:04:51,279 --> 00:04:52,439
Earn it first.

115
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:54,780
You called me "honey", though.

116
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:57,079
That doesn't count.

117
00:04:58,240 --> 00:04:59,600
How does that not count?

118
00:04:59,959 --> 00:05:01,199
Because I said so. End of story.

119
00:05:01,759 --> 00:05:02,519
Alright, you win.

120
00:05:02,959 --> 00:05:04,000
Speaking of which,

121
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:06,279
let's visit our old campus.

122
00:05:06,839 --> 00:05:09,160
Maybe we'll find
those old feelings waiting for us.

123
00:05:12,600 --> 00:05:13,199
Master.

124
00:05:16,100 --> 00:05:17,040
Why are you here again?

125
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:18,920
I told you I'd be back, Master.

126
00:05:19,060 --> 00:05:20,079
Who said I'm your master?

127
00:05:21,079 --> 00:05:21,839
Hurry up.

128
00:05:21,839 --> 00:05:23,230
We're running late for card night.

129
00:05:24,079 --> 00:05:25,079
You should get going.

130
00:05:28,399 --> 00:05:28,759
Here.

131
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:31,079
Thanks.

132
00:05:31,439 --> 00:05:31,839
Enjoy.

133
00:05:31,839 --> 00:05:32,600
Head straight home

134
00:05:33,079 --> 00:05:34,160
once you finish eating.

135
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:35,920
I'm not taking on any disciples.

136
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:36,279
Besides,

137
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:38,959
your dad doesn't want you near me.

138
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:40,839
This is between you and me.

139
00:05:40,839 --> 00:05:41,850
Why bring my dad into it?

140
00:05:42,399 --> 00:05:43,720
Too late. I've already chosen you.

141
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:45,160
Why though?

142
00:05:45,519 --> 00:05:46,480
I want to learn from you.

143
00:05:46,879 --> 00:05:49,120
You're the toughest opponent
I've ever faced.

144
00:05:49,519 --> 00:05:51,399
Once I've learned your tricks,

145
00:05:51,879 --> 00:05:52,680
we'll fight again.

146
00:05:52,730 --> 00:05:53,680
That's when I beat you.

147
00:06:16,662 --> 00:06:17,700
(Men's Toilet)

148
00:06:22,639 --> 00:06:23,759
What's wrong with you?

149
00:06:44,399 --> 00:06:44,959
Master!

150
00:06:50,060 --> 00:06:51,600
You're really not giving up, are you?

151
00:06:51,639 --> 00:06:52,000
Yeah.

152
00:06:54,879 --> 00:06:55,560
Fine. I'm in.

153
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:56,240
But there's a catch.

154
00:06:56,240 --> 00:06:57,240
Alright. Name it.

155
00:06:57,480 --> 00:06:58,319
Your dad's approval.

156
00:06:58,800 --> 00:06:59,399
That's easy.

157
00:06:59,590 --> 00:07:00,519
I'll ask him right now.

158
00:07:00,680 --> 00:07:01,360
Whatever it is,

159
00:07:01,360 --> 00:07:02,240
he'll say yes.

160
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:03,600
I wouldn't bet on it.

161
00:07:03,839 --> 00:07:05,000
You'll see.

162
00:07:07,079 --> 00:07:09,519
Dad, I really want him
to teach me martial arts.

163
00:07:09,519 --> 00:07:10,839
Just give us the green light.

164
00:07:11,160 --> 00:07:12,680
Aoxue, don't be ridiculous.

165
00:07:13,079 --> 00:07:15,360
If you're serious about it,
I'll hire you a real pro.

166
00:07:15,639 --> 00:07:16,879
I can get you

167
00:07:16,879 --> 00:07:18,079
the best teachers in the world.

168
00:07:18,680 --> 00:07:19,480
No!

169
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:20,560
I don't care!

170
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:21,639
It has to be him!

171
00:07:21,800 --> 00:07:22,959
He's better than all of them!

172
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:24,639
You silly girl.

173
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:26,759
Are you really that dead-set on him?

174
00:07:26,759 --> 00:07:27,759
Yes, I am.

175
00:07:28,439 --> 00:07:29,560
He's got real skill,

176
00:07:29,959 --> 00:07:30,900
and he's honorable.

177
00:07:30,900 --> 00:07:31,979
He even saved my life.

178
00:07:33,012 --> 00:07:33,959
The rest are just

179
00:07:34,399 --> 00:07:36,560
fame-hungry drunks and womanizers.

180
00:07:37,079 --> 00:07:38,079
They're total creeps.

181
00:07:38,550 --> 00:07:39,190
Dad,

182
00:07:39,190 --> 00:07:40,160
you should've seen it.

183
00:07:40,450 --> 00:07:42,700
Even with all the gifts
Song Wanting brought,

184
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:44,199
he didn't care.

185
00:07:44,360 --> 00:07:45,199
Everyone else

186
00:07:45,199 --> 00:07:47,240
is just desperate to suck up
to us, right?

187
00:07:47,879 --> 00:07:49,279
But he treats me like anyone else.

188
00:07:49,519 --> 00:07:50,639
Tell me he isn't special.

189
00:07:52,839 --> 00:07:54,680
Dad, I'm begging you!

190
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:55,800
Alright. Fine.

191
00:07:56,920 --> 00:07:57,360
Now,

192
00:07:58,040 --> 00:07:58,759
bring him here.

193
00:07:59,199 --> 00:08:01,112
I want a word with him.

194
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:02,519
For real?

195
00:08:02,750 --> 00:08:04,000
You said it. No taking it back.

196
00:08:04,839 --> 00:08:06,560
You really are the best dad ever!

197
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:07,399
Enough.

198
00:08:07,750 --> 00:08:09,279
- I'll go find him right now.
- Okay.

199
00:08:22,519 --> 00:08:23,120
Nice tea.

200
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:25,040
Can I get a bigger cup next time?

201
00:08:25,519 --> 00:08:26,500
This is barely a sip.

202
00:08:28,279 --> 00:08:29,000
Let's get to it.

203
00:08:29,959 --> 00:08:31,680
Have you find out who poisoned Aoxue?

204
00:08:34,399 --> 00:08:36,040
I still haven't pinned down

205
00:08:36,040 --> 00:08:38,240
when exactly the incense was swapped.

206
00:08:39,360 --> 00:08:40,840
I've got Dong looking into it.

207
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:42,000
But don't worry.

208
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:44,879
Once I have a name,

209
00:08:46,360 --> 00:08:47,720
they're dead meat.

210
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:50,240
So, Mr. Qin, did you call me over

211
00:08:50,812 --> 00:08:52,850
to hand over the medicine formula?

212
00:08:54,500 --> 00:08:56,500
That formula was entrusted to me
by an old friend.

213
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:59,039
I'll never give it to you.

214
00:09:00,759 --> 00:09:01,440
However.

215
00:09:03,080 --> 00:09:04,480
I can offer you

216
00:09:04,480 --> 00:09:05,799
something far more valuable.

217
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:07,840
She's worth

218
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:09,159
infinitely more

219
00:09:09,350 --> 00:09:11,519
to me than any formula.

220
00:09:12,639 --> 00:09:13,720
Divorce your wife

221
00:09:14,240 --> 00:09:15,000
and marry Aoxue.

222
00:09:15,600 --> 00:09:17,240
I want you as my son-in-law.

223
00:09:19,960 --> 00:09:21,559
Why are you old-timers so obsessed

224
00:09:21,559 --> 00:09:22,837
with arranged marriages?

225
00:09:23,799 --> 00:09:24,639
If you just say yes,

226
00:09:26,039 --> 00:09:27,200
all our assets

227
00:09:27,320 --> 00:09:28,039
and resources

228
00:09:28,875 --> 00:09:30,365
will be at your disposal.

229
00:09:30,925 --> 00:09:32,440
It's the 21st century, for God's sake.

230
00:09:32,679 --> 00:09:34,375
Are you really trying
to buy her a husband?

231
00:09:34,812 --> 00:09:37,092
You want justice for Madam Li,
don't you?

232
00:09:37,487 --> 00:09:38,480
Then marry Aoxue

233
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:40,137
and live under my roof.

234
00:09:40,200 --> 00:09:41,480
There's no better inside track

235
00:09:42,112 --> 00:09:44,762
to dig up dirt on me
than being my son-in-law.

236
00:09:47,759 --> 00:09:49,360
I see. You know the poisoner

237
00:09:49,360 --> 00:09:50,519
is no amateur,

238
00:09:51,480 --> 00:09:53,679
so you want me close enough

239
00:09:53,679 --> 00:09:55,080
to protect Aoxue at every turn.

240
00:09:55,480 --> 00:09:57,080
You're as sharp as I thought.

241
00:09:59,399 --> 00:10:00,080
You're right.

242
00:10:00,440 --> 00:10:01,600
It takes real power

243
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:04,840
to poison Aoxue under my roof

244
00:10:05,112 --> 00:10:06,754
and get away with it.

245
00:10:07,159 --> 00:10:08,080
I'm willing

246
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:11,279
to place my bets on you instead.

247
00:10:13,279 --> 00:10:15,759
I know whoever sent you for that formula

248
00:10:16,919 --> 00:10:17,840
is a heavy hitter, too.

249
00:10:18,759 --> 00:10:20,000
But I'm sure

250
00:10:20,320 --> 00:10:22,279
I can beat their offer,

251
00:10:22,679 --> 00:10:24,000
as long as you join my side,

252
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:24,879
keep Aoxue safe,

253
00:10:25,300 --> 00:10:26,279
and stay out of trouble.

254
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:27,960
From now on,

255
00:10:28,879 --> 00:10:30,600
forget about that formula.

256
00:10:37,337 --> 00:10:39,354
Give it some serious thought.

257
00:10:40,350 --> 00:10:41,557
I'm in no hurry for an answer.

258
00:10:44,600 --> 00:10:46,559
What's there to think about?
It's a no-brainer.

259
00:10:46,559 --> 00:10:48,279
I told you I'll handle it my way.

260
00:10:48,279 --> 00:10:49,559
The method doesn't matter

261
00:10:49,559 --> 00:10:50,679
as long as you get

262
00:10:50,679 --> 00:10:51,720
the result.

263
00:10:53,399 --> 00:10:54,080
Mr. Ye,

264
00:10:54,720 --> 00:10:56,879
this is a golden opportunity.

265
00:10:57,639 --> 00:10:58,390
As the saying goes,

266
00:10:58,799 --> 00:11:00,200
you can't make an omelette

267
00:11:00,519 --> 00:11:01,759
without breaking eggs.

268
00:11:02,440 --> 00:11:04,120
Cut the fancy talk.

269
00:11:04,799 --> 00:11:06,480
I'm not in the mood for that.

270
00:11:07,360 --> 00:11:08,919
Fine. But what about your wife?

271
00:11:09,162 --> 00:11:10,684
What has she got to do with this?

272
00:11:10,879 --> 00:11:12,279
Everything.

273
00:11:12,799 --> 00:11:14,399
We still haven't cleared Qin Gang

274
00:11:14,639 --> 00:11:16,200
of Madam Li's murder.

275
00:11:16,700 --> 00:11:18,559
He's as ruthless as they come.

276
00:11:18,559 --> 00:11:19,399
What is to stop him

277
00:11:20,080 --> 00:11:21,679
from getting rid of your wife

278
00:11:21,679 --> 00:11:23,200
just to get you into his family?

279
00:11:26,720 --> 00:11:27,360
Mr. Ye,

280
00:11:28,759 --> 00:11:29,679
why don't we just

281
00:11:30,320 --> 00:11:31,360
play along with their plan?

282
00:11:32,039 --> 00:11:34,039
Marry Qin Aoxue to get close to him,

283
00:11:34,390 --> 00:11:36,080
find the killer,
and get the formula back.

284
00:11:36,679 --> 00:11:37,279
You can

285
00:11:38,279 --> 00:11:39,879
always remarry Churan

286
00:11:40,279 --> 00:11:41,399
when the dust settles.

287
00:11:52,500 --> 00:11:54,825
(Marriage Renewal Agreement:
Ye Chen & Xiao Churan)

288
00:12:09,025 --> 00:12:11,394
Mr. Tang,
the marriage announcement is ready.

289
00:12:12,500 --> 00:12:13,490
Are we really posting it?

290
00:12:14,360 --> 00:12:14,919
Post it.

291
00:12:16,100 --> 00:12:17,279
(Xiao Family's Son-In-Law Dumps Wife
for Qin heiress)

292
00:12:17,639 --> 00:12:18,720
(Certified top-tier scumbag)

293
00:12:18,720 --> 00:12:19,399
(A two-timing son-in-law?)

294
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:36,879
Dad, Mom,

295
00:12:37,240 --> 00:12:38,320
is Churan home yet?

296
00:12:38,759 --> 00:12:39,480
Chen,

297
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:40,919
what's going on?

298
00:12:40,919 --> 00:12:43,080
Weren't things going well with you two?

299
00:12:43,080 --> 00:12:44,360
Why this, all of a sudden?

300
00:12:45,039 --> 00:12:46,000
Isn't it obvious?

301
00:12:46,399 --> 00:12:47,279
Men are all the same.

302
00:12:47,279 --> 00:12:48,200
They never stay loyal!

303
00:12:48,480 --> 00:12:49,440
One taste of success

304
00:12:49,759 --> 00:12:51,480
and they're looking for an upgrade!

305
00:12:53,512 --> 00:12:53,872
I...

306
00:12:54,425 --> 00:12:56,399
I can't explain it right now.

307
00:12:56,512 --> 00:12:58,000
Just let me see Churan.

308
00:12:58,000 --> 00:12:59,039
Why?

309
00:12:59,240 --> 00:13:00,480
To twist the knife?

310
00:13:00,799 --> 00:13:01,639
Here are your bags.

311
00:13:01,639 --> 00:13:03,879
I've packed everything you own.

312
00:13:04,137 --> 00:13:06,029
Go enjoy your new life
with the Qin family.

313
00:13:06,159 --> 00:13:07,200
We're done with you.

314
00:13:11,200 --> 00:13:12,120
It's better this way.

315
00:13:12,612 --> 00:13:14,037
Me being around

316
00:13:14,759 --> 00:13:16,120
just makes everything harder.

317
00:13:17,559 --> 00:13:18,039
Dad, Mom,

318
00:13:18,519 --> 00:13:19,519
take care of yourselves.

319
00:13:21,480 --> 00:13:22,519
You're really leaving?

320
00:13:22,720 --> 00:13:23,399
Good riddance!

321
00:13:24,240 --> 00:13:26,500
We took him in for a year,
and this is the thanks we get?

322
00:13:27,000 --> 00:13:27,919
That ungrateful prick!

323
00:13:59,450 --> 00:14:00,399
What do you want?

324
00:14:00,399 --> 00:14:01,800
- Morning.
- Morning.

325
00:14:02,639 --> 00:14:05,159
There's a major ceremony
at Buckingham Palace tomorrow.

326
00:14:05,600 --> 00:14:06,240
Have you heard?

327
00:14:08,399 --> 00:14:09,559
Who hasn't?

328
00:14:10,620 --> 00:14:11,759
I'm inviting you personally.

329
00:14:15,450 --> 00:14:16,200
Are you sure?

330
00:14:16,650 --> 00:14:17,799
Of course.

331
00:14:18,720 --> 00:14:20,799
Both Ye Chen and I want you there.

332
00:14:23,639 --> 00:14:24,200
Fine.

333
00:14:24,879 --> 00:14:26,000
Tell him

334
00:14:26,725 --> 00:14:27,720
I'll be there.

335
00:14:47,575 --> 00:14:50,063
♪They said I was only meant
to gaze at the light♪

336
00:14:50,150 --> 00:14:53,903
♪Never knowing I am the flame itself♪

337
00:14:54,363 --> 00:14:59,300
♪I am fireworks, not a fire cast aside♪

338
00:14:59,463 --> 00:15:01,750
♪I open my eyes amid the ruins♪

339
00:15:02,063 --> 00:15:04,743
♪No one shields me
from the wind or the sky♪

340
00:15:05,813 --> 00:15:08,438
♪Let them mock, let them sneer♪

341
00:15:08,738 --> 00:15:11,750
♪I sharpen my silence into blades♪

342
00:15:11,950 --> 00:15:15,000
♪Every cold word, I remember♪

343
00:15:15,113 --> 00:15:18,075
♪Etching my path of defiance
into my heart♪

344
00:15:18,343 --> 00:15:21,500
♪Fate did not sign my future for me♪

345
00:15:21,725 --> 00:15:25,475
♪I carved my own light
with clenched fists♪

346
00:15:25,475 --> 00:15:28,338
♪I belong to no one♪

347
00:15:28,400 --> 00:15:31,850
♪I am the ember
that refuses to bow to destiny♪

348
00:15:31,850 --> 00:15:34,525
♪Even if the world burns me into ash♪

349
00:15:34,525 --> 00:15:40,863
♪I will rise upon those ashes♪
